<p><a name="Bibliography" id="Bibliography"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Expert_system&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Bibliography">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Bibliography</span></h2>
